{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775901586863,"sessionID":"ses_28406c2a0ffebaRCAelXVCmpr2","part":{"id":"prt_d7bf9504c0016JJIu9OSa5w4jB","messageID":"msg_d7bf93e48001npBBDYIPTepPHq","sessionID":"ses_28406c2a0ffebaRCAelXVCmpr2","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_9380643dfb514374a7fcb5a8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project in the current working directory. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure (top-level directories and key files)\n2. What documentation exists (look in docs/, README, etc.)\n3. What the project does (check package.json, main entry points, etc.)\n4. Any existing API definitions or architecture documentation\n\nSearch thoroughly for:\n- Any docs/ directory and its contents\n- README files\n- Architecture-related files (ARCHITECTURE.md, design docs, etc.)\n- API-related files (api.md, openapi, swagger, etc.)\n- Source code structure to understand what modules exist\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of:\n- Project purpose and structure\n- All documentation files found (with paths)\n- Key modules/components in the codebase\n- Any existing API or architecture documentation content","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2840698d1ffe7BEdMUfyOQW7yh (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nI now have a comprehensive understanding of the AgentCube project. Here is the complete summary:\n\n---\n\n## AgentCube Project -- Comprehensive Summary\n\n### 1. Project Purpose\n\n**AgentCube** is a **Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents**. It:\n\n- Provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand\n- Routes HTTP traffic to sandboxes through session-aware proxies\n- Manages complete sandbox lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup)\n- Provides secure code execution capabilities for AI workloads\n\nThe project is hosted at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` and is part of the Volcano ecosystem.\n\n---\n\n### 2. Top-Level Project Structure\n\n```\nagentcube/\n├── .github/workflows/          # CI/CD workflows\n├── bin/                        # Compiled Go binaries\n├── changes/                    # Change logs\n├── ci-cd/                      # CI/CD configuration\n├── cli-toolkit/                # CLI toolkit shared specs\n├── client-go/                  # Generated Kubernetes client\n├── cmd/                        # Go binary entry points (5 binaries)\n│   ├── agentd/                 # Idle cleanup controller\n│   ├── cli/                    # Python CLI tool\n│   ├── picod/                  # Code execution daemon\n│   ├── router/                 # Session-aware HTTP proxy\n│   └── workloadmanager/        # K8s controller for sandbox lifecycle\n├── code-execution/             # Code execution module\n├── coverage.out                # Go test coverage output\n├── delta-spec.md               # Delta specification\n├── deployment/                 # Deployment design docs\n├── design.md                   # Python SDK test design (AR-040)\n├── docker/                     # Dockerfiles (3 images)\n├── docs/                       # Docusaurus documentation site\n├── example/                    # Example projects (e.g., pcap_analyzer)\n├── go.mod / go.sum             # Go module definition (Go 1.25)\n├── hack/                       # Code generation scripts\n├── idle-cleanup/               # Idle cleanup module\n├── integrations/               # External integrations (Dify plugin)\n├── Makefile                    # Build system (Go, Docker, Helm, Python)\n├── manifests/                  # Kubernetes manifests + Helm charts\n├── pkg/                        # Go packages (7 packages)\n├── project.md                  # OpenSpec project context\n├── proposal.md                 # Architecture/API documentation proposal (AR-043)\n├── python-sdk/                 # Python SDK (agentcube package)\n├── sandbox-orchestration/      # Sandbox orchestration module\n├── session-routing/            # Session routing module\n├── session-store/              # Session store module\n├── tasks.md                    # Task breakdown (AR-023)\n├── test_spec.md                # Test specification\n├── test/                       # Test utilities\n└── testing/                    # Testing infrastructure\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. All Documentation Files Found\n\n#### Docusaurus Documentation Site (`docs/`)\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/intro.md` | Project introduction and overview |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/getting-started/installation.md` | Installation guide |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/getting-started/quick-start.md` | Quick start tutorial (5-min setup) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/getting-started/configuration.md` | Configuration guide |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/architecture/overview.md` | High-level system architecture |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/architecture/components.md` | Deep dive into core components |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/architecture/session-routing.md` | Session routing mechanism |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/architecture/sandbox-lifecycle.md` | Sandbox lifecycle states and transitions |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/api-reference/control-plane.md` | WorkloadManager REST API (386 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/api-reference/data-plane.md` | Router + PicoD API (369 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/api-reference/crds.md` | Kubernetes CRD reference (224 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/user-guide/code-interpreter.md` | Code interpreter user guide |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/user-guide/agent-runtime.md` | Agent runtime user guide |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/user-guide/cli.md` | CLI reference |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/integrations/dify-plugin.md` | Dify plugin integration guide |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/integrations/langchain.md` | LangChain integration guide |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/sidebars.ts` | Docusaurus sidebar configuration |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docusaurus.config.ts` | Docusaurus site configuration |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/design.md` | Docs site design document |\n\n#### Root-Level Design/Spec Documents\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md` | OpenSpec project context (tech stack, architecture summary) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` | Python SDK unit test design (AR-040, 618 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md` | Architecture + API documentation proposal (AR-043, 249 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md` | CLI invoke/status task breakdown (AR-023, 185 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` | Delta specification |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test_spec.md` | Test specification |\n\n#### Sub-Project Docs\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/design.md` | Python SDK design document |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/spec.md` | Python SDK specification |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/integrations/design.md` | Integrations design document |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/integrations/spec.md` | Integrations specification |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/integrations/dify-plugin/README.md` | Dify plugin README |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design.md` | Deployment design |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/spec.md` | Deployment specification |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design-e2e.md` | E2E deployment design |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/client-go.md` | Client-go deployment notes |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/example/pcap_analyzer/README.md` | PCAP analyzer example README |\n\n---\n\n### 4. Key Modules/Components\n\n#### Go Binaries (5 components, built via `cmd/`)\n\n| Binary | Package | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|---------|\n| **router** | `pkg/router/` (21 files) | Session-aware HTTP proxy using Gin framework, port 8080 |\n| **workloadmanager** | `pkg/workloadmanager/` (handler/, middleware/, reconciler/, response/) | K8s controller using controller-runtime for sandbox lifecycle |\n| **agentd** | `pkg/agentd/` (3 files) | Idle cleanup controller that reclaims unused sandboxes |\n| **picod** | `pkg/picod/` (13 files) | Code execution daemon inside sandbox pods (JWT auth, file ops, command execution) |\n| **cli** | `cmd/cli/` (Python) | Python CLI tool built with Typer |\n\n#### Go Packages (7 packages under `pkg/`)\n\n| Package | Files | Purpose |\n|---------|-------|---------|\n| `pkg/router/` | 21 | HTTP proxy, session management, load balancing, JWT middleware, health checks |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/` | 4 subdirs | CRD reconciliation, HTTP handlers, middleware, response formatting |\n| `pkg/agentd/` | 3 | Idle sandbox detection and cleanup reconciler |\n| `pkg/picod/` | 13 | Code execution engine, file management, JWT authentication, sanitization |\n| `pkg/store/` | 9 | Session store abstraction with Redis and Valkey backends |\n| `pkg/apis/` | 2 subdirs | CRD type definitions (`agents/v1alpha1/`, `runtime/v1alpha1/`) |\n| `pkg/common/` | 1 subdir | Shared type definitions |\n\n#### Python SDK (`python-sdk/agentcube/`)\n\n| Module | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `code_interpreter.py` | High-level CodeInterpreterClient facade (161 lines) |\n| `agent_runtime.py` | High-level AgentRuntimeClient facade (79 lines) |\n| `clients/control_plane.py` | WorkloadManager HTTP client (96 lines) |\n| `clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | Router data plane client for code execution (176 lines) |\n| `clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | Router data plane client for agent runtime (80 lines) |\n| `exceptions.py` | Exception hierarchy (AgentCubeError, CommandExecutionError, etc.) |\n| `utils/http.py` | HTTP session creation utility |\n| `utils/utils.py` | Token reading utility |\n| `utils/log.py` | Logger utility |\n\n#### Kubernetes CRDs (4 types)\n\n| CRD | API Group | Version | Purpose |\n|-----|-----------|---------|---------|\n| **AgentRuntime** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | v1alpha1 | Long-running agent service templates |\n| **CodeInterpreter** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | v1alpha1 | Code execution sandbox templates (with warm pool support) |\n| **Sandbox** | `agents.x-k8s.io` | v1alpha1 | Individual sandbox pod instances |\n| **SandboxClaim** | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | v1alpha1 | Warm pool claim mechanism |\n\n---\n\n### 5. API Documentation Content\n\n#### Control Plane API (WorkloadManager, port 8081)\n\n| Endpoint | Method | Description |\n|----------|--------|-------------|\n| `/api/v1/sandboxes` | POST | Create a new sandbox session |\n| `/api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID` | GET | Get sandbox status by session ID |\n| `/api/v1/sandboxes` | GET | List all sandboxes (with filtering) |\n| `/api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID` | DELETE | Delete a sandbox session (idempotent) |\n| `/api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID/extend` | POST | Extend sandbox TTL |\n| `/health/live` | GET | Liveness probe |\n| `/health/ready` | GET | Readiness probe |\n\n#### Data Plane API (Router, port 8080)\n\n| Endpoint | Method | Description |\n|----------|--------|-------------|\n| `/v1/namespaces/:ns/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | GET/POST | Proxy to AgentRuntime sandbox |\n| `/v1/namespaces/:ns/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | GET/POST | Proxy to CodeInterpreter sandbox |\n| `/health/live` | GET | Router liveness |\n| `/health/ready` | GET | Router readiness |\n\n#### PicoD Internal API (inside sandbox pods)\n\n| Endpoint | Method | Description |\n|----------|--------|-------------|\n| `/api/execute` | POST | Execute a command in the sandbox |\n| `/api/files` | POST | Upload files (multipart or JSON base64) |\n| `/api/files` | GET | List files in a directory |\n| `/api/files/*path` | GET | Download a file (streaming) |\n| `/health` | GET | PicoD health check |\n\n---\n\n### 6. Architecture Documentation Content\n\nThe architecture documentation covers:\n\n- **System Architecture**: Loosely coupled microservices on Kubernetes with shared Redis/Valkey session store\n- **Design Principles**: K8s-native, session-aware, isolation-first, event-driven, horizontally scalable\n- **Component Details**: Router (Gin/Go), WorkloadManager (controller-runtime), PicoD (code execution), Agentd (cleanup), Session Store (Redis/Valkey)\n- **Session Routing**: Session creation, lookup, expiration, load balancing, error handling\n- **Sandbox Lifecycle**: 7-state model (Pending -> Creating -> Ready -> Active -> Draining -> Terminating -> Deleted)\n- **Data Flow**: Client -> Router -> Redis -> WorkloadManager -> K8s API -> Pod -> Router\n- **Security**: JWT RS256 authentication, K8s TokenReview, RBAC, network isolation\n\n---\n\n### 7. Tech Stack Summary\n\n| Layer | Technology |\n|-------|-----------|\n| **Language (server)** | Go 1.25 |\n| **Language (CLI/SDK)** | Python >= 3.10 |\n| **HTTP Framework** | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI) |\n| **Kubernetes** | CRDs, controller-runtime, sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox |\n| **Storage** | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\n| **Auth** | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\n| **Packaging** | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\n| **Docs** | Docusaurus 3.x with custom MDX components (ApiEndpoint, K8sResource) |\n| **Testing** | Go testing, pytest, miniredis |\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2840698d1ffe7BEdMUfyOQW7yh","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775901435691,"end":1775901586859}}}}
